<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Create a story or share your thoughts</title>
    <% include partials/head.ejs %>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="container">
            <blockquote>
                <h3>Hi, <code><%=session.username%></code>. Create a story by providing the following details:</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>Story title.</li>
                    <li>Upload an image to <a target="_blank" href="http://www.imgur.com">imgur</a> and provide us the direct
                        link, we prefer a 640*360 px image.</li>
                    <li>A quick summary of your story, what it's all about.</li>
                    <li>Story content.</li>
                </ol>
            </blockquote>

            <blockquote>
                <h3>If you are curious to see how your story will be shown take a look at this <a target="_blank" href="/stories/johnathons-story">story</a></h3>
            </blockquote>

            <blockquote>
                <h3>Don't have anything to share? Check these <a href="/stories">stories</a></h3>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br /><br />

    <div class="row">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="col-lg-10">
                <form action="/add-story" method="post">

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Title</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <input type="text" name="title" required class="form-control" placeholder="Story Title" />

                        </div>

                    </div>
                    <br /><br /><br />

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Image Link</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <input type="text" name="imageLink" required class="form-control" placeholder="Upload the image to imgur and put the direct link here" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <br /><br />

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Summary</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <textarea class="form-control" required name="summary" rows="4" placeholder="A short description"></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Post</label>
                        <div class="col-lg-10">
                            <textarea name="content" id="storyContent" required rows="8" class="form-control"></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-sm-offset-6 col-sm-6">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit your story</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br /><br />
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $('#storyContent').summernote({
                height: 250,
                toolbar: [
                    ['style', ['bold', 'italic', 'underline', 'clear']],
                    ['font', ['strikethrough', 'superscript', 'subscript']],
                    ['fontsize', ['fontsize']],
                    ['color', ['color']],
                    ['para', ['ul', 'ol', 'paragraph']],
                    ['height', ['height']],
                    ['link', ['linkDialogShow', 'unlink']],
                    ['table', ['table']]
                ]
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>